.TH "ORG.BLUEZ.THERMOMETERWATCHER" "5" "July 2011" "BlueZ" "Linux System Administration"
.SH NAME
org.bluez.ThermometerWatcher \- BlueZ D-Bus Health Thermometer Watcher API documentation
.SH INTERFACE
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B Service
unique name
.TP
.B Interface
org.bluez.ThermometerWatcher1
.TP
.B Object path
freely definable
.UNINDENT
.SS Methods
.SS void MeasurementReceived(dict measurement)
.sp
This callback gets called when a measurement has been
scanned in the thermometer.
.sp
Possible measurement values:
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B int16 Exponent
.TP
.B int32 Mantissa
Exponent and Mantissa values as extracted from float value defined by
IEEE\-11073\-20601.
.sp
Measurement value is calculated as
(Mantissa) * (10^Exponent)
.sp
For special cases Exponent is
set to 0 and Mantissa is set to
one of following values:
.UNINDENT
